name: "Canary Plays Dead (Alt. Vers.)" by Richard F. Yates (Holy Fool)
description: [Various pens on paper with digital embellishments...] I honestly have no idea what's happening in this piece. I see a bird playing dead, and a snake surrounded by a weird aura, and some strange individual reaching for either the bird or the snake...or the viewer! Who knows? ---Richard F. Yates (Holy Fool)
